Subject: drm/xe/vm: tidy up xe_runtime_pm usage
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 2d30332a5ec004effe24d669003bf94e7f167387
